                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Price</ln>
                        <fn>George</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Asks that the women of Staunton contribute cloth to the hospital at
                    Manassas Junction.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Vote in Western Virginia</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>States that the vote in the trans-Allegheny portion of the Virginia showed
                    a majority of counties for secession by a vote of 39 to 22.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look>x</look>
            </div>
